按抚，解决不了最后问题。他的思维，是八面玲珑。似乎是不用战争，解决战争才能解决的问题，实际上是自欺欺人而矣。最终，国民党还会是扶不起的阿斗流水落花春去也。台湾问题，必须武力收复。", "pid": "3905389126630595", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905392725500006", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601646, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "建议领袖"}], "name": "正东迎朝阳"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "211569189", "dep": 0, "text": "蔡英文上位，尽管不会立即实施台独，但一定会不予余力，并且一定会成为美日制华的恶狗。台海风平浪静的日子也将可能结束。其祸在两岸，其利在美日，不可不察。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905389277732166", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446600825, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "长江水木"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1560456151", "dep": 0, "text": "对比当年国共姿态言行，今日之国民党更是腌臜狭隘。有过之无不及，哪里有三民主义的影子。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905389487706968", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446600874, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "大熊EMC"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5718474853", "dep": 0, "text": "不期而遇不签协议不发声明，这几句是说给台湾人听的，排除阻力之举，重点是国民党和马英九终于下决心为自己也为选举，把两岸关系向前推动的一大步，两岸领导人互动，这是件大事，对中国统一，两岸和平的大事，为以后无论和民进党还是国民党的交流都推上一个更高的阶段，可喜可贺，要体谅马英九体谅对方", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905390293462053", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601067, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "敏感之防霉"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5745070744", "dep": 0, "text": "这是两岸的大事，小马哥能在最后时候看清形式，这也是台湾的幸事，客观上也拉了一把gmd。下一步就看会不会动员在大陆的台商回去投票了。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905391655967072", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601392, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "睡懒觉的光头强"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1868851987", "dep": 0, "text": "这也是权宜，马和国民党不可能不顾及岛内的接受度，慢慢来，不急，也急不得。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905392364699046", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601561, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "冷思考"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2300426417", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905392419379596", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601574, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "漂亮的涛涛姐"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2161707254", "dep": 0, "text": "一笑了之", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905393489133110", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446601829, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "兰花之叶"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2133097445", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905394373595373", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446602039, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "怡水深"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1661321682", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905394541974179", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446602080, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "第一时间穿越"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1218981057", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905403954238232", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446604324, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "岩礁58"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2280126722", "dep": 0, "text": "谈比不谈好。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905404276673715", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446604401, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "劲舟007"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5747103357", "dep": 0, "text": "中国可以先出手", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905411063095165", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446606019, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "第27维"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1265416255", "dep": 0, "text": "十七年驻闽经历，要起作用了。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905413512476272", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446606602, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "江津问渡"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5118987767", "dep": 0, "text": "赖狗扶不上墙的国民党，真心无法让人乐观，普世自由民主的大便和自身的僵化完全让国民党变成了吃屎的傻逼蠢逼，就看马娘娘能不能抓住这根稻草了[挖鼻]", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905417183049141", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446607477, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "天地大萝卜"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1348200744", "dep": 0, "text": "台湾地区领导要求国家领导人在国际场合见面，表面看起来是为了保护自己的尊严，实际上还是向世界宣告台湾是与大陆平起平坐的中华民国，遭到中共拒绝是理所当然的事，因为不拒绝，就意味着默许台湾的独立。但这次为了给马先生一个和谈机会，习总还是以民族大义为重，做了最大让步，同意在新加坡会面。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905417752660762", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446607613, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "中国汤奋志"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1859494613", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905420064249362", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446608165, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "上图老保安"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "3357624132", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905422240757272", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446608683, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "_老四哥_"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5680658570", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905426959318698", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446609808, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "溜达溜达小超人"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2214950473", "dep": 0, "text": "让台独分子闹去吧，闹的凶了，大陆会收拾那些龟孙子的。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 1, "mid": "3905431200017868", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1446610819, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2156679410", "dep": 0, "text": "冬来天欲雪！可饮一杯无？干杯吧！ ", "pid": "3905431200017868", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905434090429015", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446611508, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "树鸣www"}], "name": "长空鸣雁"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1995056405", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905449407068796", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446615160, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "lele宇翔"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "5555901979", "dep": 0, "text": "117新加坡马习会后，估计马在返台后的记者会上，又会强调这是对等，没有矮化台。马的“身份”也的确是个问题，一再坚持不让步的话，讨不了一点好处，不坚持呢，又怕在岛内政治圈没法混，揪心吧[笑cry]大陆放出一个中国的框架下啥都可以谈的表态后，马在身份问题上还是让步了的～后续真的啥都可谈？", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905461147767314", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446617960, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "原海20150314"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2059528641", "dep": 0, "text": "这是做给台独民进党看的，只要在九二共识下什么都可以谈，包括两岸领导人之间也可以往来；反之，不承认九二共识，一切免谈，在全世界都在关注和参与一路一带时，台湾则会被踢出局，加速边缘化，台湾的经济和民生将会继续倒退。也提醒岛民选票要慎重。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905467442927965", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446619461, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "乐水喜山"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2273270202", "dep": 0, "text": "在台湾本土化、去中国化两大关键问题上，国民党、民进党本质上都相差无几。只是一个明显，一个做得隐蔽一些。这次大选国民党本土大佬硬逼“换柱”就很说明问题。国民党和大陆搞好关系为的是捞好处，並不会真正同意统一〔包括将来〕。拖下去台湾和大陆只会渐行渐远。台湾只能武力解决，而且越快越好。", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905477723191495", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446621911, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "茫茫原上青青草"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "2864135900", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905489223808227", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446624654, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "泽晋吴"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1362028432", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905498481012380", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446626861, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "枫林秋露"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1362028432", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905499110294435", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446627010, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "枫林秋露"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1964965597", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905506487646381", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1446628770, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "天马101"}, {"evtlist": [877], "uid": "1780942090", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3905387054678449", "tr": 0, "mid": "3905513135683727", "times": 1, "chil